csExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6108216\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_6108216\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nzz1707817327409.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nzz1707817327409.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nzz1707817327409.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bdw1665702578600\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__selectcase_case_endselectcase_238373\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Define a block of conditional case selections.\n </p>\n<p class=\"lines\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">selectcaseMatchExpression <br/>    {caseExpression1{, Expression11 {, Expression1N} } <br/>        ... zero or more ProcScript statements ... <br/>    {caseExpression2{, Expression21 {, Expression2N} } <br/>        ... zero or more ProcScript statements ... <br/>... <br/>    {elsecase <br/>        ... zero or more ProcScript statements ... } <br/>endselectcase</var></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__topic_d50607e1_d50608e1_d50609e1_d50610e1_d50611e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1082481e60\">Clauses </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7355e1_d7356e1_d7357e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Clauses</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7355e1_d7356e1_d7357e1__entry__1\">Qualifier</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7355e1_d7356e1_d7357e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7355e1_d7356e1_d7357e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">case</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7355e1_d7356e1_d7357e1__entry__2\">Marks the beginning of a conditional block of\n                        ProcScript to be evaluated. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7355e1_d7356e1_d7357e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">elsecase</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7355e1_d7356e1_d7357e1__entry__2\">\n Marks the ProcScript to be executed if none of the case expressions match <var class=\"keyword varname\">MatchExpression</var>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7355e1_d7356e1_d7357e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endselectcase</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7355e1_d7356e1_d7357e1__entry__2\">Marks the end of the case definitions. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__topic_d50612e1_d50613e1_d50614e1_d50615e1_d50616e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1082481e133\">Parameters </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7358e1_d7359e1_d7360e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7358e1_d7359e1_d7360e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7358e1_d7359e1_d7360e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7358e1_d7359e1_d7360e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7358e1_d7359e1_d7360e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">MatchExpression</var>, <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7358e1_d7359e1_d7360e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bdw1665702578600__table_d7358e1_d7359e1_d7360e1__entry__3\">\n Expressions to evaluate. They can evaluate to any data type. Data type conversion may be performed to allow a proper comparison to be made. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vee1714313798310.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vee1714313798310.html\" title=\"The ProcScript language enables you to convert data from one type to another, perform arithmetic operations, extract data values, and perform string substitution. Uniface carries out implicit type conversion whenever necessary, for example, when assignments are made between non-matching data types or when comparing non-matching data types. The ProcScript language also provides a number of functions that allow you to convert from one data type to another.\">Data Handling in ProcScript</a>.\n                             </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__topic_d50617e1_d50618e1_d50619e1_d50620e1_d50621e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1082481e197\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__d5966e20\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__topic_d50622e1_d50623e1_d50624e1_d50625e1_d50626e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1082481e207\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__topic_d50627e1_d50628e1_d50629e1_d50630e1_d50631e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1082481e216\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__p_d77027e1_d77028e1_d77029e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">selectcase</span> statement defines a series of conditional blocks of ProcScript. Each block is defined as a case.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__p_d77030e1_d77031e1_d77032e1\">The <var class=\"keyword varname\">MatchExpression</var> is compared to the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>s on each <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">case</span> statement in turn. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">MatchExpression</var>=<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> is <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">TRUE</span>, the ProcScript statements in that block (up to the next <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">case</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">elsecase</span>, or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endselectcase</span> statement, are executed). If no <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> matches <var class=\"keyword varname\">MatchExpression</var>, the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">elsecase</span> clause is executed.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__p_d77033e1_d77034e1_d77035e1\">If several cases are to be handled in the same manner, you can put multiple expressions on the case statement. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">selectcase vCase\n case 1, 2, 3\n <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScript</var>\n case 4\n <var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScript</var>\n elsecase\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ProcScript</var>\nendselectcase</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__p_d77036e1_d77037e1_d77038e1\">A <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">selectcase</span>/<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endselectcase</span> block is equivalent to the following <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">if</span>/<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endif</span> block:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">if</span><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">(</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">MatchExpression</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression1</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">)</span>\n     ... \n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">elseif</span><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">(</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">MatchExpression</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression2</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">)</span>\n     ... \n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">elseif</span><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">(</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">MatchExpression</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span><var class=\"keyword varname\">ExpressionN</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">)</span>\n     ... \n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">else</span>\n   ... \n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">endif</span>\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__section_vqc_t3p_k1c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1082481e350\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">selectcase</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example illustrates the possibilities of the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">selectcase</span> statement:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bdw1665702578600__pre_xb4_53p_k1c\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">selectcase vVariable\n case \"\" ;an empty string\n message \"vVariable is empty\"\n case \"ABC\" ;a string\n message \"vVariable is ABC\"\n case \"abc\" ;a string\n message \"vVariable is abc\"\n case 'a*' ;a syntax string\n message \"vVariable matches syntax a*\"\n case \"DEF%%$2XYZ%%%\" ;a string\n message \"vVariable is DEF%%$2XYZ%%%\"\n case 123 ;an ordinary number\n message \"vVariable is 123\"\n case 1.23e_+13 ;a floating point number\n message \"vVariable is 1.23e_+13\"\n case MYFIELD.MYENTITY ;a field with value \"abc\"\n message \"vVariable is abc\"\n case $date ;a date\n message \"vVariable is today\"\n case $date + 7 ;a date\n message \"vVariable is one week from today\"\n elsecase\n message \"vVariable is not what we expected\"\nendselectcase\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sfr1707816914621.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>if</a><p>Define an if/endif conditional block.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/unf1665702578355.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>repeat</a><p>Define a repeat/until loop.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwa1707817649603.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>while</a><p>Define a while/endwhile loop.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jbm1707818341035.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Operators</a><p>Operators perform arithmetic, relational, logical, string manipulation, struct member de-reference, operation de-reference, and field indirection operations in ProcScript instructions.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6108216\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6108216\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "selectcase Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define a block of conditional case selections. selectcaseMatchExpression {caseExpression1{, Expression11 {, Expression1N} } ... zero or more ProcScript statements ... {caseExpression2{, Expression21 {, Expression2N} } ... zero or more ProcScript statements ... ... {elsecase ... zero or more ProcScript statements ... } endselectcase Clauses Table 1. Clauses Qualifier Description case Marks the beginning of a conditional block of ProcScript to be evaluated. elsecase Marks the ProcScript to be executed if none of the case expressions match MatchExpression . endselectcase Marks the end of the case definitions. Parameters Table 2. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description MatchExpression , Expression String Expressions to evaluate. They can evaluate to any data type. Data type conversion may be performed to allow a proper comparison to be made. For more information, see Data Handling in ProcScript . Return Values None Use Allowed in all component types. Description The selectcase statement defines a series of conditional blocks of ProcScript. Each block is defined as a case. The MatchExpression is compared to the Expression s on each case statement in turn. If MatchExpression = Expression is TRUE , the ProcScript statements in that block (up to the next case , elsecase , or endselectcase statement, are executed). If no Expression matches MatchExpression , the elsecase clause is executed. If several cases are to be handled in the same manner, you can put multiple expressions on the case statement. For example: selectcase vCase case 1, 2, 3 ProcScript case 4 ProcScript elsecase ProcScript endselectcase Copy A selectcase / endselectcase block is equivalent to the following if / endif block: if ( MatchExpression = Expression1 ) ... elseif ( MatchExpression = Expression2 ) ... elseif ( MatchExpression = ExpressionN ) ... else ... endif Copy Example: Using selectcase The following example illustrates the possibilities of the selectcase statement: selectcase vVariable case \"\" ;an empty string message \"vVariable is empty\" case \"ABC\" ;a string message \"vVariable is ABC\" case \"abc\" ;a string message \"vVariable is abc\" case 'a*' ;a syntax string message \"vVariable matches syntax a*\" case \"DEF%%$2XYZ%%%\" ;a string message \"vVariable is DEF%%$2XYZ%%%\" case 123 ;an ordinary number message \"vVariable is 123\" case 1.23e_+13 ;a floating point number message \"vVariable is 1.23e_+13\" case MYFIELD.MYENTITY ;a field with value \"abc\" message \"vVariable is abc\" case $date ;a date message \"vVariable is today\" case $date + 7 ;a date message \"vVariable is one week from today\" elsecase message \"vVariable is not what we expected\" endselectcase Copy Related Links if Define an if/endif conditional block. repeat Define a repeat/until loop. while Define a while/endwhile loop. Operators Operators perform arithmetic, relational, logical, string manipulation, struct member de-reference, operation de-reference, and field indirection operations in ProcScript instructions. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}